，p = pressure壓力，F= force作用力，S = surface area表面面積，即係話表面面積愈細，壓力就愈大，所以用劍嘅壓力可能重大過用鎗砲<br />\n加上佢用迴力鏢有機會係打中關節位，係比較脆弱嘅部分<br />\n<br />\n可以睇吓下面例子:<br />\nNotice that the sharp knife has a very small area of contact with the surface, while the dull knife has a much larger area of contact. If both knives are pushed down with the same force, the sharp knife will exert a much greater pressure on the surface than the dull knife - and pressure cuts.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.batesville.k12.in.us/physics/PhyNet/Mechanics/Newton2/Pressure.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.batesville.k12.in.us%2Fphysics%2FPhyNet%2FMechanics%2FNewton2%2FPressure.html&d=qAUHm39efqk3lQPpkVvpYP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ac25c0ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.batesville.k12.in.us/physics/PhyNet/Mechanics/Newton2/Pressure.html</a>"}]}